{"tid":630404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日生日","createTime":"2018-04-15T14:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T15:11:05.000Z","uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7889e23af641346fe7ac3cbfa947f3b60a3bca93","tid":630404,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日生日 ，同老母去食飯<br />\n食完飯老母話去買個蛋糕<br />\n我係店出面等，之後聽到老母同收銀個店員講，個仔咁大生日都唔同人出去玩下<br />\n果下唔知點解，個人好似有種說不出聲既感覺<br />\n我知老母一直擔心我無朋友<br />\n其實我只係鐘意獨處多啲姐<br />\n但其實我又真係無個知心好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b2e4221f6b95892d26a1e5c39d3aeb79c82a62","tid":630404,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"5歲過後再無慶祝過生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都算好過我嫁啦"},{"pid":"1e7a3560950bd40988c850e5eb9abdadff4ea1ce","tid":630404,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b2e4221f6b95892d26a1e5c39d3aeb79c82a62","tid":630404,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"5歲過後再無慶祝過生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都算好過我嫁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404ffcb69c667fb172b0f48b0c8bf1b9e757b1d9","tid":630404,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"我唔係話我生日過得唔好<br />\n只係老母擔心我果下 個心好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1fefabe2a93db97b95ec08de87518dad75334a","tid":630404,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5歲過後再無慶祝過生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\